Imports System
  Public Class Calculator
    Public Function Calculate() as String
    Dim result As String = ""
    Dim FV As String = "var3".Replace(".", "")
    Dim BV As String = "var4".Replace(".", "")
    If FV.Length <4 Then
    For i As Integer = 0 to 3 - FV.Length
    FV = FV & "0"
    Next
    End If
    If BV.Length <4 Then
    For i As Integer = 0 to 3 - BV.Length
    BV = BV & "0"
    Next
    End If
    result = "var1".Substring(0, 8) & "var2" & "-" & FV.Substring(0, 4) & "-" & BV.Substring(0, 4)
    Return result
  End Function
End Class
Filter1: 料號,增層層別,正面面積,背面面積
Filter2:
Dim FV As String = Var3.Replace(".", "")
    Dim BV As String = Var4.Replace(".", "")
    If FV.Length <4 Then
    For i As Integer = 0 to 3 - FV.Length
    FV = FV & "0"
    Next
    End If
    If BV.Length <4 Then
    For i As Integer = 0 to 3 - BV.Length
    BV = BV & "0"
    Next
    End If
    result = Var1.Substring(0, 8) & Var2 & "-" & FV.Substring(0, 4) & "-" & BV.Substring(0, 4)

WHERE [LayerName] = 'VarLayer'

DECLARE @Face AS varchar(5)
SET @Face = CASE WHEN 'VarFace' = '1' THEN 1 WHEN 'VarFace' = '2' THEN 0 END

SELECT 
    CASE 
        WHEN EXISTS (
SELECT TOP 1 [ChangeTIme] FROM [utchfacmrpt].[report].[dbo].[view_HIST] WITH(NOLOCK) 
WHERE [lotnum] = 'VarLot'
AND [LayerName] = 'VarLayer'
AND [ProcName] = 'VarProc'
AND [AftStatus] = 'MoveOut'
AND [BefStatus] = 'CheckOut'
        )
        THEN (
SELECT TOP 1 CAST(ISNULL(SUM([DefectQty]),0) AS varchar) AS [Qty] FROM [MES-C].[IPQC_Mapping_H3].[dbo].[RawData_Panel] AS pnl WITH(NOLOCK) 
LEFT JOIN [MES-C].[IPQC_Mapping_H3].[dbo].[RawData_Pcs] AS pcs WITH(NOLOCK) ON pnl.[RecNo] = pcs.[RecNo] 
WHERE pnl.[LotID] + pnl.[LotNo] = 'VarLot'
AND pnl.[Side] = @Face
AND [LayerName] = 'VarLayer'
AND pnl.[ProcNo] = '41'
AND TRIM(pcs.[ItemName]) = 'printing shift(印刷偏移)'
        )
        ELSE ''
    END

AND [LayerName] = 'VarLayer'
AND [ProcName] = 'VarProc'

        )

WHERE pnl.[LotID] + pnl.[LotNo] = 'VarLot'
AND pnl.[Side] = @Face
AND [LayerName] = 'VarLayer'
AND pnl.[ProcNo] = '57'
AND TRIM(pcs.[ItemName]) = 'Water Mark(水紋)'
        )
        ELSE ''
    END

Imports System
  Public Class Calculator
    Public Function Calculate() as String
    Dim result As String = ""
    Dim FV As String = "var3".Replace(".", "")
    Dim BV As String = "var4".Replace(".", "")
    If FV.Length <4 Then
    For i As Integer = 0 to 3 - FV.Length
    FV = FV & "0"
    Next
    End If
    If BV.Length <4 Then
    For i As Integer = 0 to 3 - BV.Length
    BV = BV & "0"
    Next
    End If
    result = "var1".Substring(0, 8) & "var2" & "-" & FV.Substring(0, 4) & "-" & BV.Substring(0, 4)
    Return result
  End Function
End Class

FROM [10.44.65.110].[SPC_PPT].[dbo].[Var_Data] AS a WITH (NOLOCK)

	  INNER JOIN [10.44.65.110].[SPC_PPT].[dbo].[Var_File] AS d WITH (NOLOCK) ON c.[FileID] = d.[FileID]

	  INNER JOIN [10.44.65.110].[SPC_PPT].[dbo].[Var_Ctrl] AS c WITH (NOLOCK) ON b.[CtrlID] = c.[CtrlID]
	  INNER JOIN [10.44.65.110].[SPC_PPT].[dbo].[Var_File] AS d WITH (NOLOCK) ON c.[FileID] = d.[FileID]
	  INNER JOIN [10.44.65.110].[SPC_PPT].[dbo].[Var_FileGroup] AS e WITH (NOLOCK) ON d.[FileGroupID] = e.[FileGroupID]

AND e.[FileGroupName] = '15MDL_機械鑽孔'
AND d.[FileName] = '15MDL_SUEP_ETCHING AMOUNT_EQP'

SELECT ROUND(AVG([Data]),3)AS [Data] 
FROM(
SELECT AVG(CONVERT(float,[Item1])) AS [Item1]
      ,AVG(CONVERT(float,[item2])) AS [Item2]
      ,AVG(CONVERT(float,[item3])) AS [Item3]
      ,AVG(CONVERT(float,[item4])) AS [Item4]
      ,AVG(CONVERT(float,[item5])) AS [Item5]
      ,AVG(CONVERT(float,[item6])) AS [Item6]
      ,AVG(CONVERT(float,[item7])) AS [Item7]
      ,AVG(CONVERT(float,[item8])) AS [Item8]
      ,AVG(CONVERT(float,[item9])) AS [Item9]
  FROM [H3_Systematic].[dbo].[MRX_SourceData] nolock
  WHERE [procCode] = 'VarProc' AND [Lot] LIKE 'VarLot%' AND [LayerName] = 'VarLayer'
  GROUP BY [procCode],[Lot],[LayerName]) p
  UNPIVOT
  (
  [Data]  FOR [Ori] IN ([Item1],[Item2],[Item3],[Item4],[Item5],[Item6],[Item7],[Item8],[Item9])
  ) upv
